description:
Really want to apologize for my absences as of late and mostly my inconsistencies. You guys mean more than the world to me and I feel like I have really been letting not only you guys down but myself down as well. I am working on getting myself together but in the meantime I WILL NOT be skipping days like that anymore, and the quest for building this PC begins.

As of July 10th 2015, I now have the PC. You all are legends.
